PN,39901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773256283
OL,3,C'Misleading' weather icons 'costing UK
OL,4,Cattractions millions'
OL,6,FOne of the UK's most popular tourist
OL,7,Fdestinations, Chester Zoo, is leading
OL,8,Fa nationwide campaign against weather
OL,9,Fapps, claiming that "misleading" rain
OL,10,Ficons are costing the visitor economy
OL,11,Fmillions of pounds every year.
OL,13,FThe zoo has coordinated a joint appeal
OL,14,Fto the Met Office on behalf of more
OL,15,Fthan 80 major outdoor attractions -
OL,16,Fincluding the Eden Project, Blackpool
OL,17,FPleasure Beach, and Blenheim Palace.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
