OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773256283
OL,3,C'Misleading' weather icons 'costing UK
OL,4,Cattractions millions'
OL,6,FThey argue that a single raincloud
OL,7,Ficon used to summarise a 24-hour
OL,8,Fperiod often creates the false
OL,9,Fimpression of a "washout," even when
OL,10,Fthe vast majority of the day is dry.
OL,12,FIndustry leaders warn that these small
OL,13,Fdigital symbols are triggering a
OL,14,F"disproportionate economic hit," with
OL,15,Fsome venues reporting a 30% drop in
OL,16,Fvisitors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773256283
OL,3,C'Misleading' weather icons 'costing UK
OL,4,Cattractions millions'
OL,6,FThey say, for many families, the
OL,7,Fdecision to head out is made
OL,8,Fspontaneously. Research suggests
OL,9,Faround 70% of people check a forecast
OL,10,Fbefore leaving the house.
OL,12,FThe group stresses they are not
OL,13,Fquestioning the accuracy of the data,
OL,14,Fbut rather how it is presented.
OL,16,FThey say third-party apps often
OL,17,Fdisplay a rain symbol for an entire
OL,18,Fday based on a brief shower at 6am or
OL,19,Frain that occurs overnight, which
OL,20,Fcould cost large venues "up to
OL,21,F#137,000 a day."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773256283
OL,3,C'Misleading' weather icons 'costing UK
OL,4,Cattractions millions'
OL,6,FChief Operating Officer of Chester
OL,7,FZoo, Dom Strange, said the current
OL,8,Fsystem is failing both businesses and
OL,9,Fthe public.
OL,11,F"When families see a raincloud icon,
OL,12,Fmany simply stay home," he said. "The
OL,13,Freality might be a brief shower at 6am
OL,14,F-but the symbol suggests a washout."
OL,16,FHe continued to say: "...we're
OL,17,Fspeaking up for the wider visitor
OL,18,Feconomy - from heritage sites to theme
OL,19,Fparks - and the thousands of jobs that
OL,20,Fdepend on spontaneous visits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773256283
OL,3,C'Misleading' weather icons 'costing UK
OL,4,Cattractions millions'
OL,6,F"The Met Office is the UK's most
OL,7,Ftrusted weather authority and in a
OL,8,Funique position to help lead the way
OL,9,Fon clearer forecasting so other apps
OL,10,Ffollow their leads.
OL,12,F"With today's data and technology,
OL,13,Fthere's an opportunity to present
OL,14,Fforecasts in a way that better
OL,15,Freflects how the day will actually
OL,16,Ffeel on the ground."
OL,18,FThe coalition is now calling for a
OL,19,Fformal roundtable with the Met Office,
OL,20,Fthe government, and app developers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773256283
OL,3,C'Misleading' weather icons 'costing UK
OL,4,Cattractions millions'
OL,6,FThey want to see separate symbols for
OL,7,Fdaytime and overnight weather, written
OL,8,Fsummaries that use phrases like
OL,9,F"showers early, brighter later" and
OL,10,Fdry time indicators.
OL,12,FOlly Reed, from tourism consultancy
OL,13,FNavigate, said the data is consistent
OL,14,Facross heritage sites, gardens, and
OL,15,Ftheme parks: "Bookings don't just
OL,16,Fshift with the weather itself, they
OL,17,Fshift with how that weather is framed."
OL,19,FITV News has contacted the Met Office
OL,20,Ffor comment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
